#$Id: INSTALL,v 1.1 2003/03/27 15:17:54 andrei Exp $

Compilation
-----------

./configure ; make

(if you want to regenerate configure.in and all the Makefile.in you should
 run first ./bootstrap but you need decently recent versions of autoconf, 
 automake & libtool)


Installation
------------

make install


Other usefull targets
---------------------

make dist-gzip     - tar.gz  archive
make dist-bzip2    - tar.bz2 archive
make distclean     - cleans everything configure generated
